<h3 class="topic">Materials</h3>
<p>
  Available inks include Black, Blue, Green, Yellow, Bright Red, and Mahogany. The MZ990
  model can *usually* print 2 inks in one pass with great results, so both one and two color
  projects are quick and easy to produce.
</p>

